## Additional Terms

### Data Privacy
This tool processes financial consolidation data locally on your computer. No data
is transmitted to external servers or third parties. Users are responsible for 
ensuring compliance with their organization's data security and privacy policies.

### Usage Context
This tool is designed specifically for audit and financial consolidation scoping
purposes. Users are responsible for validating output and ensuring it meets their
specific audit and compliance requirements.

### No Warranty
This software is provided without warranty of any kind. While every effort has been
made to ensure reliability and accuracy, users should validate all output and use
the tool at their own risk.

